            {{#markdown}}
```xml
<!-- This tag should be a child of the body -->
<div class="win-alert-stack">

    <div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade in" role="alert">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true"><i class="win-icon-cancel"></i></span>
        </button>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-24">
                    Alert example, <a href="#">click here</a>.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- We can stack other alert components here -->
</div>
```
            {{/markdown}}

            <p>The required JavaScript to initialize the <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/javascript/#affix" target="_blank">Affix Boostrap component</a>:</p>

            {{#markdown}}
```javascript
$(function () {
    var alertStack = $('.win-alert-stack');

    if (alertStack.length == 0) {
        return;
    }

    alertStack.affix({
        offset: {
            top: alertStack.offset().top
        }
    });
});
```
